### Remaining Jenkins balance

* The remaining Jenkins project balance was discussed, as the project
  representatives wanted it donated to OSUOSL. It was determined that this
  should be fine as both SPI and OSUOSL are USA 501(c)(3) charitable
  organizations and OSUOSL provides services relied on by the Jenkins project.


