## Other business

* The board discussed publication of the services inventory, to include which
  organizations are donating those services to SPI, for which there was
  consensus so long as it was made clear this is not an endorsement of those
  services nor organizations.
* A quick summary was provided covering concerns raised by the Advisory Board
  for The Document Foundation about transactions made by their project's own
  Board of Directors, but which do not directly affect SPI.


